	<article class="post-156899 post type-post status-publish hentry category-disunion tag-brazil tag-civil-war-us-1861-65 tag-immigration-and-emigration tag-slavery-historical des-civil-war-us-1861-65 des-immigration-and-emigration des-slavery-historical geo-brazil news_keywords-american-civil-war news_keywords-brazil news_keywords-immigration-2 news_keywords-slavery" id="post-156899">
	<header class="postHeader">
				<div class="postKicker">
			<span class="kicker"><a href="//opinionator.blogs.nytimes.com/category/disunion/?module=BlogCategory&version=Blog Post&action=Click&contentCollection=Opinion&pgtype=Blogs&region=Header">Disunion</a></span>
